OL,3,CPeak family ferry trips can cost up to
OL,4,C48% more on DFDS than Condor
OL,6,FThe cost of a family of four
OL,7,Ftravelling to the UK and France by
OL,8,Fferry for a week's summer holiday can
OL,9,Fbe almost 50% more expensive from
OL,10,FJersey than Guernsey.
OL,12,FITV News has compared the prices of a
OL,13,Fone-week return trip on DFDS and
OL,14,FCondor Ferries across each calendar
OL,15,Fweek in August, for two adults, two
OL,16,Fchildren and a car.
OL,18,FDFDS currently only offer a non-
OL,19,Frefundable "economy ticket".
