OL,3,CPeak family ferry trips can cost up to
OL,4,C48% more on DFDS than Condor
OL,6,FThe closest Condor equivalent for
OL,7,Fthese trips is its "saver" rate where
OL,8,Fpassengers can cancel up to 48 hours
OL,9,Fbefore to get 75% of their money back.
OL,11,FDespite Jersey being closer to St Malo
OL,12,Fand DFDS offering an introductory 10%
OL,13,Fdiscount on all services, the company
OL,14,Fstill charges much more than Condor
OL,15,Ffor these sailings.
OL,17,FDFDS is 48.5% more expensive across
OL,18,Fthe first three weeks of August and
OL,19,Fjust over a third pricier in the final
OL,20,Ffull week.
