OL,6,FPrices correct as of 25 February.
OL,8,FIn response, DFDS says it operates
OL,9,F"dynamic pricing, which means prices
OL,10,Fwill vary depending on travel dates
OL,11,Fand vehicle types".
OL,13,FIt explains: "Analysis has shown that
OL,14,Fsavings will be made for certain trips
OL,15,Fand on others, the price will be
OL,16,Fhigher.
