OL,4,C48% more on DFDS than Condor
OL,6,F"As operations progress, DFDS will be
OL,7,Flooking to incorporate a customer
OL,8,Floyalty programme for frequent
OL,9,Ftravellers, discounted offers and
OL,10,Fadditional benefits."
OL,12,FChris Parker, DFDS Jersey Route
OL,13,FDirector, adds: "For Jersey, and this
OL,14,Fis quite important, there is a much
OL,15,Fbigger range of departures available
OL,16,Fto get to St Malo.
OL,18,F"There's over 150 more sailings from
OL,19,FJersey to St Malo and back between
OL,20,FMarch and September than Guernsey, for
OL,21,Fexample.
